## btf2go validation: Pass rate dropped for tier {{tier.name}}

**What triggered:** `btf2go.validation.tier.pass_rate` for tier **{{tier.name}}** fell below 1.0 (100%) in the last 30 minutes. One or more ELF files in this tier are now failing code generation.

**Affected tier(s):** {{tier.name}}

**Dashboard:** https://us3.datadoghq.com/dashboard/2n5-36z-3rc/btf2go-validation

**Remediation:** Inspect the tier-level findings on the dashboard ("Per-tier pass rate" widget). Look for recently merged changes that may have broken the generator for this tier's ELF patterns.

